title: Final Football Friday For 2015 Season
text:
Final Football Friday For 2015 Season October 16, 2015, 4:58 AM SIOUX FALLS, SD - 
It's the last Football Friday for South Dakota high school athletes this season. 
The final games of the regular season are next Thursday, October 22. 
For week 7, KELOLAND Sports will be covering games from across the area. Our livestream game of the week will be 11AA #5 Brookings at 11AA #3 Harrisburg. Kickoff is scheduled for 7 p.m. 
Here's a look at the matchups we're covering: 9B #4 Dell Rapids St. Mary @ 9A #3 Colman-Egan (Viewers' Game Of The Week) 11AAA Rapid City Stevens @ 11AAA #1 Washington 11AA Huron @ 11AAA #3 O'Gorman 11AAA #4 Brandon Valley @ 11AAA #5 Lincoln 11A #1 Madison @ 11A Tea Area 11A #4 West Central @ 11B #5 Tri-Valley 11A #5 Belle Fourche @ 11A #2 St. Thomas More 9AA #2 Wolsey-Wessington @ 9AA #1 Woonsocket/Wessington Springs/Sanborn Central 
Watch for highlights on KELOLAND SportsZone at 10:30 p.m. on Friday. 
Share your pictures and videos with us by emailing ushare@keloland.com ; submitting a photo using the KELOLAND News App ; upload it to the uShare Photo Gallery ; or use #kelosports when you post on Facebook, Twitter or Instagram. Sports Resources
